default&#xa0;
defaultQ.8  What role should the BBC play in developing technology and new ways of delivering output?default8.1
default              
defaultThe BBC has traditionally played a leading role in developing new technologies. We believe it to be in the 
defaultlicence fee payers’ interests that this should continue, delivering new opportunities to enjoy BBC content.
default8.2
default              
defaultThe BBC should stay at the forefront and maintain an understanding of the possibilities that are being developed elsewhere.
